
jFuzzyDate

 jFuzzyDate is a lightweight java library for formatting easily readable time
 distances and dates.
 
 Examples: 
 
	* A duration of "16d 02:30:40" may formatted as "two weeks".
	
	* Looking about 50 days in the past may be formatted to "two months ago".
 
